New Poolparty map with some extensions Big Grin! \:D.
PS: v3 was made by me too Happy \:\) (If your wondered that they look similar in some way ^^)

Put the BSP file into your
X:\...\...\Steam\SteamApps\...\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
Folder
or add it to your map content server (If your own a server I'am sure your know how XD XD )

-=Features=-

-Board of the tower and some other stone things are destroyable ( 200 hp )
-Deages in the sidepool
